  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nRun Nethermind compiled from `master` with hybrid pruning parameters, and restart it before it is synchronized fully from mainnet. This leads to DB corruption.\r\n\r\n`Nethermind/v1.12.4-48-211fa1a25-20220208/X64-Linux/6.0.1`\r\n\r\nStarted with:\r\n```\r\n      - --Pruning.Mode\r\n      - Hybrid\r\n      - --Pruning.FullPruningTrigger\r\n      - VolumeFreeSpace\r\n```\r\n\r\nErrors seen after restart:\r\n\r\n```\r\nexecution_1  | 2022-02-08 15:42:23.7699|Sync mode update failed RocksDbSharp.RocksDbException: Corruption: bad entry in block\r\nexecution_1  |    at RocksDbSharp.Native.rocksdb_get(IntPtr db, IntPtr read_options, Byte[] key, Int64 keyLength, ColumnFamilyHandle cf) in /nethermind/src/rocksdb-sharp/RocksDbSharp/Native.Wrap.cs:line 109\r\nexecution_1  |    at Nethermind.Db.FullPruning.FullPruningDb.get_Item(Byte[] key) in /nethermind/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Db/FullPruning/FullPruningDb.cs:line 71\r\nexecution_1  |    at Nethermind.Synchronization.ParallelSync.SyncProgressResolver.IsFullySynced(Keccak stateRoot) in /nethermind/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Synchronization/ParallelSync/SyncProgressResolver.cs:line 83\r\nexecution_1  |    at Nethermind.Synchronization.ParallelSync.SyncProgressResolver.SearchForFullState(BlockHeader startHeader) in /nethermind/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Synchronization/ParallelSync/SyncProgressResolver.cs:line 123\r\nexecution_1  |    at Nethermind.Synchronization.ParallelSync.SyncProgressResolver.FindBestFullState() in /nethermind/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Synchronization/ParallelSync/SyncProgressResolver.cs:line 96\r\nexecution_1  |    at Nethermind.Synchronization.ParallelSync.MultiSyncModeSelector.TakeSnapshot(UInt256& peerDifficulty, Int64 peerBlock) in /nethermind/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Synchronization/ParallelSync/MultiSyncModeSelector.cs:line 533\r\nexecution_1  |    at Nethermind.Synchronization.ParallelSync.MultiSyncModeSelector.Update() in /nethermind/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Synchronization/ParallelSync/MultiSyncModeSelector.cs:line 188\r\nexecution_1  |    at Nethermind.Synchronization.ParallelSync.MultiSyncModeSelector.TimerOnElapsed(Object sender, ElapsedEventArgs e) in /nethermind/src/Nethermind/Nethermind.Synchronization/ParallelSync/MultiSyncModeSelector.cs:line 247\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe corrupted DB is small yet, ~20 GiB. Let me know whether it's of use to you, and I'll upload it to cloud storage somewhere.\r\n",
